{"title":"微思集","authors":["胡仲仟"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"微思集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡仲仟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭露丑，是一种美；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为丑在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以美需要保护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"量一个人的真正高度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是脱去高跟和高帽子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是缺乏生命力的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越爱装腔作势。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花，在黑暗中也是香的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子，在泥土中也是活的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金，在垃圾中也是夺目的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫得醒死人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却叫不醒装死的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容貌美丑，与镜子无关；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品格高低，与职位无关；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能大小，与年龄无关；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理有无，与权力无关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主子睡着了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴才还要从鼾声中寻找意义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀附在树干上的藤萝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时比树干爬得还高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能总是默默地行走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要像飓风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生出咆哮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要像波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出怒吼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}